# AVAssetExportPresetPassthrough

**Global Variable**

A preset to export the asset in its current format, unless otherwise prohibited.

## Declaration

```swift
let AVAssetExportPresetPassthrough: String
```

## Discussion

This option doesn’t show up in the [doc://com.apple.avfoundation/documentation/AVFoundation/AVAssetExportSession/allExportPresets()] and [doc://com.apple.avfoundation/documentation/AVFoundation/AVAssetExportSession/exportPresets(compatibleWith:)] methods.
